text: Bak Ji-yun (, born September 21, 1992) is a South Korean judoka. She competed at the 2016 Summer Olympics in the women's 63 kg event, in which she was eliminated in the first round by Alice Schlesinger. ==References== Category:1992 births Category:Living people Category:South Korean female judoka Category:Olympic judoka of South Korea Category:Judoka at the 2016 Summer Olympics Category:Judoka at the 2014 Asian Games Category:Asian Games medalists in judo Category:Asian Games silver medalists for South Korea Category:Medalists at the 2014 Asian Games Category:Universiade medalists in judo Category:Universiade silver medalists for South Korea Category:Medalists at the 2015 Summer Universiade
